api.body:
require "pixcHelper"
require "pixcProtocolKeyboard"
if self.lock then return end
if self.keyboard ~= nil then
	self.lock = true
	self.uninit()
	Utils.Timer.sleep(500)
end
self.lock = nil
self.keyboard = createpixcProtocolKeyboard()
self.keyboard:create(self.IsOpen)
self.keyboard:start(self.Keypress)
api.name: init

api.body:
if self.keyboard ~= nil then
	self.keyboard:close()
	self.keyboard = nil
end
api.name: uninit

api.body:
self._InOpen = pixcCommon.execAttribute(0, self._InOpen, val, doSet)
return self._InOpen
api.name: IsOpen

api.body:
if self.keyboard == nil then return end
self.keyboard:send(keyCode)
api.name: send
